HEADWORD: Utterly
<hw>Ut"ter*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an utter manner; to the full
extent; fully; totally; <as>as, <ex>utterly</ex> ruined; it is
<ex>utterly</ex> vain</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
